{"title":"Last night you left me and slept","author":{"name":"Rumi"},"publishDate":"2011-02-12","lines":[{"line":"Last night you left me and slept","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"your own deep sleep. Tonight you turn","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"and turn. I say,","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"‘You and I will be together","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"till the universe dissolves.’","stanza":1,"number":5},{"line":"You mumble back things you thought of","stanza":1,"number":6},{"line":"when you were drunk.","stanza":1,"number":7}]}